# Retrospectives are LOCAL-ONLY by default.
#
# Per-project retros often contain sensitive context: client names, business
# reasoning, internal bugs, candid self-assessment. The CHANGELOG references
# retros by filename so the trail is visible even when the documents aren't.
#
# Exceptions (tracked in git):
# - README.md                    explains the convention
# - 2026-06-llm-gateway.md       project-zero example showing what good looks like
#
# To make a future retrospective public, remove its filename from this gitignore
# (add a "!filename.md" line below the *.md rule).

*.md
!README.md
!2026-06-llm-gateway.md
